code: @Override public ByteChannel open(int socketTimeout) throws IOException {     SocketAddress address = new InetSocketAddress(this.portProvider.getPort()).     logger.trace("Opening tunnel connection to target server on " + address).     SocketChannel channel = SocketChannel.open(address).     channel.socket().setSoTimeout(socketTimeout).     return new TimeoutAwareChannel(channel). }
@Override public int read(ByteBuffer dst) throws IOException {     return this.readChannel.read(dst). }
@Override public int write(ByteBuffer src) throws IOException {     return this.socketChannel.write(src). }
@Override public void close() throws IOException {     this.socketChannel.close(). }
